"title": "5201: accusation",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5201",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A charge brought against a person in a legal, ecclesiastical or spiritual context.</p>\n<h2>In legal affairs in general</h2>\n<h3>In the OT legal systems</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut19:15-Deut19:21\">DEU 19:15–19:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut17:2-Deut17:7\">DEU 17:2–17:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:8-1Kgs21:13\">1KI 21:8–21:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra4:6\">EZR 4:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh5:6-Neh5:7\">NEH 5:6–5:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:4-Dan6:5\">DAN 6:4–6:5</a></p>\n<h3>In the NT legal systems</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:38-Acts19:41\">ACT 19:38–19:41</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:1\">ACT 7:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:12-Acts18:13\">ACT 18:12–18:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:23-Acts23:30\">ACT 23:23–23:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts24:1-Acts24:9\">ACT 24:1–24:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts25:1-Acts25:2\">ACT 25:1–25:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:19\">ACT 28:19</a></p>\n<h2>In God's covenant dealings with his people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:1-Mic6:2\">MIC 6:1–6:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:5-Jer2:9\">JER 2:5–2:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos4:1-Hos4:3\">HOS 4:1–4:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos11:12-Hos12:6\">HOS 11:12–12:6</a></p>\n<h2>In the earthly experience of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:6\">JHN 19:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:12-Matt27:14\">MAT 27:12–27:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:37\">MAT 27:37</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:26\">MRK 15:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:38\">LUK 23:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:19-John19:22\">JHN 19:19–19:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:4\">LUK 23:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:29\">JHN 18:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:4\">JHN 19:4</a></p>\n<h2>In the experience of God's people</h2>\n<h3>In the context of justification</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:33\">ROM 8:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa50:8-Isa50:9\">ISA 50:8–50:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:22\">COL 1:22</a></p>\n<h3>In their standing in the eyes of the world</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:3-Eph5:4\">EPH 5:3–5:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:16\">MAT 5:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:13\">1TH 3:13</a></p>\n<h2>In the conduct of church affairs</h2>\n<h3>Christian involvement in litigation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:25-Matt5:26\">MAT 5:25–5:26</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:58-Luke12:59\">LUK 12:58–12:59</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:1-1Cor6:8\">1CO 6:1–6:8</a></p>\n<h3>In the qualification for church leaders</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:2\">1TI 3:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:6\">TIT 1:6</a></p>\n<h3>In church disputes</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:19\">1TI 5:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:15-Matt18:20\">MAT 18:15–18:20</a></p>\n<h2>In the character and activity of Satan</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech3:1-Zech3:2\">ZEC 3:1–3:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:9-Job1:11\">JOB 1:9–1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps109:6\">PSA 109:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:9-Rev12:10\">REV 12:9–12:10</a></p>",
